        {
            "id": 6439986,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 交易台(TTD-US)大漲5.04%，報24.78美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>交易台(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TTD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TTD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TTD-US</a>)截至台北時間01日23:48股價上漲1.19美元，報24.78美元，漲幅5.04%，成交量7,532,676（股），盤中最高價24.78美元、最低價24.02美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.08%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.66%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+1.31%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.44%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>交易台(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TTD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TTD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TTD-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+4.29%</li> <li>近 1 月：+7.18%</li> <li>近 3 月：-22.22%</li> <li>近 6 月：-51.83%</li> <li>今年以來：-37.86%</li></ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6439986",
